drupalNodeEvent.title: U.S.-China Trade Tension and Technology Distrust

field_description.processed: On September 30, SupChina is hosting a CEO Webinar and live China Corner Office Podcast on U.S.-China trade tensions and technology distrust, featuring the author of One Billion Customers: Lessons from the Front Lines of Doing Business in China and Greater China Chairman for APCO Worldwide James McGregor.
